{"tid":2491714,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣總統府及行政院共同譴責中港政府繼續侵害香港的民主及人權","createTime":"2021-04-16T13:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T14:35:43.000Z","uid":292499,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"da3573a178121b794ec90c5127ebb4af25c10f2e","tid":2491714,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:32:06.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒創辦人黎智英、民主黨創黨主席李柱銘等多名泛民主派人士，因2019年參與民陣發起的維園「8.18流水式集會」而被裁定組織及參與非法集結罪名成立，西九龍裁判法院於今審理判刑7名被告，黎智英被判刑1年。對此，總統府和行政院齊聲譴責，總統府呼籲北京當局，「正視香港人民的主流民意，唯有與香港人民展開誠懇對話，才能化解爭議，讓香港社會回歸平靜」。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n羅秉成指出，看到媒體報導香港將爭取自由民主的黎智英先生等人定罪判刑，深表同情與遺憾，更要再次譴責北京當局罔顧、壓迫港人爭取民主與自由的決心。而此事也讓台灣人民更加戒慎警惕，若有一天不幸被中國併吞，那台灣勢將淪為今日的香港，任人宰割。只有全國人民團結一致，堅持民主自由，堅守人權價值，才不會讓企圖以各種方式併吞台灣的中國得逞。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210416/FZZ2B46TF5HLNPRECEHJIAIKTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210416%2FFZZ2B46TF5HLNPRECEHJIAIKTQ%2F&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLTe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=03643fcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210416%2FFZZ2B46TF5HLNPRECEHJIAIKTQ%2F&h=71c9e674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210416/FZZ2B46TF5HLNPRECEHJIAIKTQ/</a>"},{"pid":"c9da226a5ef4bad59e7e895fa5a118a581266dfa","tid":2491714,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"a55ba6d40eb6d515957a2ced63eb8b94033c460f","tid":2491714,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:33:35.000Z","msg":"不如台灣又制裁下"},{"pid":"246756c01e2c58cb71ba417c95695928cbfb36ad","tid":2491714,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:34:35.000Z","msg