」。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n羅秉成指出，看到媒體報導香港將爭取自由民主的黎智英先生等人定罪判刑，深表同情與遺憾，更要再次譴責北京當局罔顧、壓迫港人爭取民主與自由的決心。而此事也讓台灣人民更加戒慎警惕，若有一天不幸被中國併吞，那台灣勢將淪為今日的香港，任人宰割。只有全國人民團結一致，堅持民主自由，堅守人權價值，才不會讓企圖以各種方式併吞台灣的中國得逞。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210416/FZZ2B46TF5HLNPRECEHJIAIKTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210416%2FFZZ2B46TF5HLNPRECEHJIAIKTQ%2F&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLTe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=03643fcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210416%2FFZZ2B46TF5HLNPRECEHJIAIKTQ%2F&h=71c9e674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210416/FZZ2B46TF5HLNPRECEHJIAIKTQ/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:40:22.000Z","msg":"仲硬過美國 敗登已經縮沙唔理支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5401daa317c25084aa4085c142a082b8d7af4eb","tid":2491714,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"587dcba4a22f982fdce395f133851957f2b00251","tid":2491714,"uid":300877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"多謝台灣朋友支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48e78f5ae8172eefb16511cb08fc0e203a6320d","tid":2491714,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:40:37.000Z","msg":"向佐: I love TW"},{"pid":"f6d9b320500e36667f9993ebe9838775cafb83e6","tid":2491714,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"172f5086873d5a00f11fa61ee9adc1506bcc5216","tid":2491714,"uid":292499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"329d388165e0a3f95d9dcde